co.cask.cdap.api.annotation
Annotation Type ProcessInput

@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface ProcessInput

Annotation tag required for Flowlet process methods.

Example: 

 
 OutputEmitter<Long> output;

 @ProcessInput
 public void round(Double number) {
   output.emit(Math.round(number));
 }

See the Cask DAP Developer Guides and the CDAP example applications for more information.

See Also:
Flowlet
